sequenceDiagram
    participant Konflux as Konflux CI<br/>(Hermetic Build)
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>Kubernetes API
    participant IS as ImageStream CR<br/>Cluster
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant NotebookCtrl as ODH Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Pod<br/>8888/TCP (Jupyter)<br/>8787/TCP (CS/RS)
    participant Nginx as nginx Proxy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Httpd as httpd CGI<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as Notebook Culler
    participant DSP as Data Science<br/>Pipelines API<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Runtime as Runtime Image<br/>(Pipeline Step)

    Note over Konflux,Registry: Flow 1: Workbench Image Deployment
    Konflux->>Registry: Push built image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount auth
    Operator->>IS: Deploy ImageStream manifests<br/>Kubernetes API, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount
    IS->>Registry: Reference image by sha256 digest<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull Secret
    Dashboard->>IS: Read opendatahub.io/* annotations<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token

    Note over User,Workbench: Flow 1 continued: User creates workbench
    User->>Dashboard: Select workbench type
    Dashboard->>NotebookCtrl: Create Notebook CR
    NotebookCtrl->>NotebookCtrl: Resolve image from<br/>ImageStream tag
    NotebookCtrl->>Workbench: Create Pod<br/>(inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar,<br/>mount CA bundles)

    Note over User,Workbench: User accesses workbench
    User->>KubeRBAC: Access workbench<br/>HTTPS/8443, OAuth
    KubeRBAC->>Workbench: Forward to IDE<br/>HTTP/8888 or HTTP/8787

    Note over Culler,Httpd: Flow 2: Idle Culling (Code-Server / RStudio)
    Culler->>KubeRBAC: GET /api/kernels/<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KubeRBAC->>Nginx: Forward<br/>HTTP/80, localhost
    Nginx->>Httpd: Proxy to CGI<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost
    Httpd->>Httpd: Execute access.cgi
    alt Code-Server
        Httpd->>Workbench: GET /codeserver/healthz<br/>HTTP/8787, localhost
        Workbench-->>Httpd: Heartbeat response
    else RStudio
        Httpd->>Nginx: Read access log<br/>File read
        Nginx-->>Httpd: last_activity timestamp
    end
    Httpd-->>Nginx: Jupyter kernel JSON
    Nginx-->>KubeRBAC: /api/kernels/ response
    KubeRBAC-->>Culler: Activity status

    Note over Workbench,Runtime: Flow 3: Elyra Pipeline Execution
    Workbench->>DSP: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTP/8888, Bearer Token
    DSP->>Runtime: Create pipeline step Pod<br/>ServiceAccount
    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute notebook cells
    Runtime-->>DSP: Step completion
